data.description: Bank owned home with 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, finished basement and 2 car attached garage in Meadowbrook with No association fees.  Entire 1st floor with hardwood floors, family room with floor to ceiling stone fireplace, Kitchen with upgraded 42" cabinets and granite counters, kitchen eating area for table space and sliders to large brick paver patio that lead to a fenced yard with shed,  2nd floor laundry area, basement with full bathroom, Master bedroom with vaulted ceiling, walk-in-closet and private bathroom with dual vanity sinks, separate shower and soaking tub. Corner lot. Sold as is where is, taxes prorated at 100% seller does not provide survey.
